ced from the client’s own land, salvaging Guanacaste and Guapinol trees. This bespoke furniture was locally produced through a meticulous two-and-a-half-year process, ensuring the highest quality and adaptability to both interior and exterior needs.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/modern-kitchen-design-180325-816-01.jpg\" alt=\"A modern white kitchen in an open plan interior.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/modern-kitchen-design-180325-816-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/modern-kitchen-design-180325-816-01-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/modern-kitchen-design-180325-816-01-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/modern-kitchen-design-180325-816-01-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/modern-kitchen-design-180325-816-01-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/modern-kitchen-design-180325-816-02.jpg\" alt=\"A modern white kitchen in an open plan interior.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/modern-kitchen-design-180325-816-02.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/modern-kitchen-design-180325-816-02-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/modern-kitchen-design-180325-816-02-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/modern-kitchen-design-180325-816-02-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/modern-kitchen-design-180325-816-02-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 